{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1580,"text":"[On April 3, 2016 we saw\nthe largest data leak in history.]"},{"time":6061,"text":"[The Panama Papers exposed\nrich and powerful people]"},{"time":8932,"text":"[hiding vast amounts of money\nin offshore accounts.]"},{"time":11828,"text":"[What does this mean?]"},{"time":15312,"text":"[We called Robert Palmer\nof Global Witness to explain.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20852,"text":"This week, there have been\na whole slew and deluge of stories"},{"time":25828,"text":"coming out from the leak\nof 11 million documents"},{"time":29148,"text":"from a Panamanian-based law firm\ncalled Mossack Fonseca."},{"time":33596,"text":"The release of these papers from Panama\nlifts the veil on a tiny piece"},{"time":39402,"text":"of the secretive offshore world."},{"time":41664,"text":"We get an insight into how clients\nand banks and lawyers"},{"time":46996,"text":"go to companies like Mossack Fonseca"},{"time":49048,"text":"and say, \"OK, we want\nan anonymous company,"},{"time":51579,"text":"can you give us one?\""},{"time":52995,"text":"So you actually get to see the emails,"},{"time":54829,"text":"you get to see the exchanges of messages,"},{"time":56816,"text":"you get to see the mechanics\nof how this works,"},{"time":59915,"text":"how this operates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61340,"text":"Now, this has already started\nto have pretty immediate repercussions."},{"time":65417,"text":"The Prime Minister\nof Iceland has resigned."},{"time":68042,"text":"We've also had news"},{"time":69281,"text":"that an ally of the brutal\nSyrian dictator Bashar Al-Assad"},{"time":74348,"text":"has also got offshore companies."},{"time":76927,"text":"There's been allegations\nof a $2 billion money trail"},{"time":82180,"text":"that leads back to President\nVladimir Putin of Russia"},{"time":86107,"text":"via his close childhood friend,"},{"time":88592,"text":"who happens to be a top cellist."},{"time":90844,"text":"And there will be a lot\nof rich individuals out there"},{"time":93468,"text":"and others who will be nervous\nabout the next set of stories"},{"time":97810,"text":"and the next set of leaked documents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100387,"text":"Now, this sounds like the plot\nof a spy thriller"},{"time":104597,"text":"or a John Grisham novel."},{"time":106284,"text":"It seems very distant\nfrom you, me, ordinary people."},{"time":110324,"text":"Why should we care about this?"},{"time":112856,"text":"But the truth is that if rich\nand powerful individuals"},{"time":117123,"text":"are able to keep their money offshore"},{"time":119801,"text":"and not pay the taxes that they should,"},{"time":122312,"text":"it means that there is less money\nfor vital public services"},{"time":126430,"text":"like healthcare, education, roads."},{"time":129807,"text":"And that affects all of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132152,"text":"Now, for my organization Global Witness,"},{"time":134892,"text":"this exposé has been phenomenal."},{"time":138978,"text":"We have the world's media\nand political leaders"},{"time":143490,"text":"talking about how individuals\ncan use offshore secrecy"},{"time":148169,"text":"to hide and disguise their assets --"},{"time":150588,"text":"something we have been talking about\nand exposing for a decade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155396,"text":"Now, I think a lot of people find\nthis entire world baffling and confusing,"},{"time":160055,"text":"and hard to understand how\nthis sort of offshore world works."},{"time":164544,"text":"I like to think of it a bit\nlike a Russian doll."},{"time":167400,"text":"So you can have one company\nstacked inside another company,"},{"time":170883,"text":"stacked inside another company,"},{"time":173018,"text":"making it almost impossible\nto really understand"},{"time":177453,"text":"who is behind these structures."},{"time":179704,"text":"It can be very difficult\nfor law enforcement"},{"time":182641,"text":"or tax authorities,\njournalists, civil society"},{"time":185628,"text":"to really understand what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188318,"text":"I also think it's interesting"},{"time":189779,"text":"that there's been less coverage\nof this issue in the United States."},{"time":193010,"text":"And that's perhaps because\nsome prominent US people"},{"time":196797,"text":"just haven't figured\nin this exposé, in this scandal."},{"time":201359,"text":"Now, that's not because\nthere are no rich Americans"},{"time":205318,"text":"who are stashing their assets offshore."},{"time":208152,"text":"It's just because of the way\nin which offshore works,"},{"time":211998,"text":"Mossack Fonseca has fewer\nAmerican clients."},{"time":215512,"text":"I think if we saw leaks\nfrom the Cayman Islands"},{"time":218792,"text":"or even from Delaware\nor Wyoming or Nevada,"},{"time":222467,"text":"you would see many more cases\nand examples linking back to Americans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228283,"text":"In fact, in a number of US states\nyou need less information,"},{"time":234225,"text":"you need to provide less\ninformation to get a company"},{"time":238423,"text":"than you do to get a library card."},{"time":241240,"text":"That sort of secrecy in America\nhas allowed employees of school districts"},{"time":247046,"text":"to rip off schoolchildren."},{"time":248976,"text":"It has allowed scammers\nto rip off vulnerable investors."},{"time":254452,"text":"This is the sort of behavior\nthat affects all of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258166,"text":"Now, at Global Witness,"},{"time":260061,"text":"we wanted to see what this\nactually looked like in practice."},{"time":263346,"text":"How does this actually work?"},{"time":265783,"text":"So what we did"},{"time":266982,"text":"is we sent in an undercover investigator\nto 13 Manhattan law firms."},{"time":273763,"text":"Our investigator posed\nas an African minister"},{"time":277561,"text":"who wanted to move suspect funds\ninto the United States"},{"time":281712,"text":"to buy a house, a yacht, a jet."},{"time":285288,"text":"Now, what was truly shocking\nwas that all but one of those lawyers"},{"time":290373,"text":"provided our investigator with suggestions"},{"time":294990,"text":"on how to move those suspect funds."},{"time":296978,"text":"These were all preliminary meetings,"},{"time":298814,"text":"and none of the lawyers\ntook us on as a client"},{"time":301110,"text":"and of course no money moved hands,"},{"time":303423,"text":"but it really shows the problem\nwith the system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306905,"text":"It's also important"},{"time":308848,"text":"to not just think about this\nas individual cases."},{"time":312238,"text":"This is not just about\nan individual lawyer"},{"time":314475,"text":"who's spoken to our undercover\ninvestigator and provided suggestions."},{"time":318353,"text":"It's not just about\na particular senior politician"},{"time":321232,"text":"who's been caught up in a scandal."},{"time":322885,"text":"This is about how a system works,"},{"time":325965,"text":"that entrenches corruption,\ntax evasion, poverty and instability."},{"time":331932,"text":"And in order to tackle this,"},{"time":333771,"text":"we need to change the game."},{"time":335466,"text":"We need to change the rules of the game"},{"time":338012,"text":"to make this sort of behavior harder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340028,"text":"This may seem like doom and gloom,"},{"time":342996,"text":"like there's nothing we can do about it,"},{"time":344941,"text":"like nothing has ever changed,"},{"time":346595,"text":"like there will always be rich\nand powerful individuals."},{"time":349955,"text":"But as a natural optimist,"},{"time":352426,"text":"I do see that we are starting\nto get some change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355928,"text":"Over the last couple of years,"},{"time":357827,"text":"we've seen a real push towards\ngreater transparency"},{"time":361519,"text":"when it comes to company ownership."},{"time":363755,"text":"This issue was put on the political agenda"},{"time":366116,"text":"by the UK Prime Minister David Cameron"},{"time":368634,"text":"at a big G8 Summit that was held\nin Northern Ireland in 2013."},{"time":373872,"text":"And since then, the European Union\nis going to be creating"},{"time":378246,"text":"central registers at a national level"},{"time":380427,"text":"of who really owns and controls\ncompanies across Europe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383858,"text":"One of the things that is sad is that,\nactually, the US is lagging behind."},{"time":388958,"text":"There's bipartisan legislation\nthat had been introduced"},{"time":391682,"text":"in the House and the Senate,"},{"time":393609,"text":"but it isn't making as much progress\nas we'd like to see."},{"time":396790,"text":"So we'd really want to see\nthe Panama leaks,"},{"time":399901,"text":"this huge peek into the offshore world,"},{"time":403719,"text":"be used as a way of opening up\nin the US and around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408795,"text":"For us at Global Witness,\nthis is a moment for change."},{"time":413950,"text":"We need ordinary people to get angry"},{"time":417722,"text":"at the way in which people\ncan hide their identity"},{"time":420999,"text":"behind secret companies."},{"time":422936,"text":"We need business leaders\nto stand up and say,"},{"time":426547,"text":"\"Secrecy like this is not\ngood for business.\""},{"time":429855,"text":"We need political leaders\nto recognize the problem,"},{"time":434259,"text":"and to commit to changing the law\nto open up this sort of secrecy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439639,"text":"Together, we can end the secrecy"},{"time":442942,"text":"that is currently allowing tax evasion,"},{"time":446023,"text":"corruption, money laundering to flourish."}]}]}